item.title: CVE-2021-4228|2024-08-03T17:23:08.901Z -- lanner%20inc -- iac-ast2500a
item.description: Use of hard-coded TLS certificate by default allows an attacker to perform Man-in-the-Middle (MitM) attacks even in the presence of the HTTPS connection. This issue affects: Lanner Inc IAC-AST2500A standard firmware version 1.00.0.
